query: SELECT p.id, p.partNumber, p.name, pc.categoryId, c.name as categoryName FROM products p LEFT JOIN product_categories pc ON p.id = pc.productId LEFT JOIN categories c ON pc.categoryId = c.id WHERE LOWER(p.name) LIKE '%vanguard%' LIMIT 10;
